    <p>Taking part in our competitions requires a significantly monetary investment from the team. To successfully compete in 2015 we need to acquire funding for parts, transportation, and entry fees. For the 2015 season, our competitions are hosted in a variety of locations across North America. Our team welcomes all forms of contribution to the team, be it financial, service-related or product-based.</p>

