	<h3>Platinum Tier (Over $3000)</h3>
	<p>At this level, you will receive all the benefits from Gold Tier, as well as a copy of out team T-Shirt. We will also hand out your company's promotional material at all our competitions.</p>

	<h3>Gold Tier ($1500-$3000)</h3>
	<p>At this level, you will receive all the benefits from Silver Tier, as well as your company's logo on our team T-Shirts. You will also receive a plaque at the end of our competition year (Summer 2015) thanking you for your sponsorship.</p>

	<h3>Silver Tier ($500-$1500)</h3>
	<p>At this level, you will receive all the benefits from Bronze Tier, as well as your company's logo on our Website and one of our robots.</p>

	<h3>Bronze Tier (Under $500)</h3>
	<p>At this level, your company name will be displayed on our website. You will receive a Sponsorship Certificate thanking you for your support, as well as an invitation to attend our competitions and a semi-annual newsletter.</p>
